<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/bidens-policies-propose-minor-changes-in-a-time-of-crisis/">Biden’s Policies Propose Minor Changes in a Time of Crisis</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Biden assured wealthy donors that under his leadership, “nothing would fundamentally change.” His policies reflect that.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/alexis-goldstein/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Alexis Goldstein</a></span>, </dd>
